  "texts": [
    "Through a systematic review using a scientometric approach [57], the study maps out the literature on DFIG-based WECS, identifies primary topics, and enhances understanding of current research paths.",
    "This paper aims to conduct a comprehensive review of the literature on DFIG-based WECS using scientometric analysis.",
    "In Sect. 2 including research methods, bibliometric examination, and scientometric analysis.",
    "In Sect. 3 presents about Key analyses include studying publication and citation trends, document co-citation analysis and clustering analysis, leading countries and collaboration networks, and author co-citation patterns.",
    "Additionally, the paper identifies high-productivity research areas, unveiling significant themes and directions within the field."
  ]
}